             MODES 

normal mode
insert mode 
... (many, many more) 

  i, I, a, A        - normal -> insert 
  ESC, C-[          - insert -> normal


          MOVING AROUND


          ^          k
        <   >      h   l
          v          j



        BASIC JUMP MOVEMENTS

  h, l               - jump by a character
  w, W, e, E         - jump by a word
  b, B               - jump by a word (backwards)
  0, $               - jump to the first / last character in line
  ^, g_              - jump to the first / last (non-blank) character in line
  gg, G              - jump to first / last line


