          CURSOR POSITION

  H, M, L            - top / middle / down of the screen
  zz                 - refocus to the middle 


          SEARCH JUMPS

  f, F                - find character (inclusive)
  t, T                - find character (exclusive)
  /                   - text search
  n, N                - next / previous occurrence

